<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MFA Enabled Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 550px;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0px 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            text-align: center;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .header {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .header::after {
            content: "";
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: #007bff;
            display: block;
            margin: 8px auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 15px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .message strong {
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Mobile-friendly adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
                max-width: 90%;
            }

            .button {
                width: 80%;
                display: block;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/120x60.png?text=Company+Logo" alt="Company Logo" class="logo">
        <p class="header">Multi-Factor Authentication Enabled</p>
        <p class="message">Hello <strong>{{username}}</strong>,</p>
        <p class="message">
            Your email <strong>{{email}}</strong> is now protected with <strong>{{type}}</strong> Multi-Factor
            Authentication (MFA).
            This adds an extra layer of security to your account.
        </p>
        <p class="message">
            If you did not enable MFA, please <strong>secure your account immediately</strong>.
        </p>
        <a href="{{security_link}}" class="button">Review Security Settings</a>
        <p class="footer">
            If you need help, contact our <a href="{{support_link}}">Support Team</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>